    "created_at": "2017-02-13T10:48:16Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-02-13T10:48:47Z",
    "body": ">I would rather that we bring windows and linux up to speed with macOS and simply fire show and hide events on minimize and restore. Semantically it would make sense.\r\n\r\nI'm fine with this as well, although I don't think we can make `show` and `hide` fire based on the occlusion state on other platforms."
